{"tid":1646959,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撞人的士狗破產令期間管有貴重私人財產、虛報收入、以及接受饋贈。","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:40:31.000Z","uid":176858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"282a65c90cc43f2a1e2d899e6150b1e50d2c49dc","tid":1646959,"uid":176858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"煲大佢<br />\n<br />\n破產管理署電子郵件： oroadmin@oro.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n本人最近留意新聞報導，發現有一宗交通意外牽涉之人士，懷疑曾經破產，而接受公眾人士饋贈。<br />\n<br />\n於2019年10月6日，一輛的士於深水埗區衝入人群，導致途人嚴重受傷，見下列網址： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191008/s00001/1570473457416/撞人遭毆的士司機稱失值14萬手表-報稱衝示威者路障「踩錯油門」-警列暴動案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191008%2Fs00001%2F1570473457416%2F%E6%92%9E%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E6%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%B1%E5%80%BC14%E8%90%AC%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8-%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E8%A1%9D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E3%80%8C%E8%B8%A9%E9%8C%AF%E6%B2%B9%E9%96%80%E3%80%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcsZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=0ad8bfc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191008%2Fs00001%2F1570473457416%2F%E6%92%9E%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E6%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%B1%E5%80%BC14%E8%90%AC%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8-%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E8%A1%9D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E3%80%8C%E8%B8%A9%E9%8C%AF%E6%B2%B9%E9%96%80%E3%80%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88&h=8f401616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191008/s00001/1570473457416/撞人遭毆的士司機稱失值14萬手表-報稱衝示威者路障「踩錯油門」-警列暴動案</a><br />\n<br />\n事後，該名司機被發現名為「鄭國泉」，見下列司機証及現場照片：<br />\n<br />\n事後，如上列《明報》報導，該名男子報稱損失現金及名錶，合共價值港幣十餘萬。另外，事後有團體高調聲明，會捐贈港幣五十二萬予該名男子，見下列報導：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1609051/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%B6%89%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%8D%9052%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E4%BA%88%E7%9A%84%E5%93%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1609051%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%258D%259052%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25BA%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2593%25A5&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcsZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=8e8336c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1609051%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%258D%259052%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25BA%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2593%25A5&h=a8044dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1609051/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%B6%89%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%8D%9052%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E4%BA%88%E7%9A%84%E5%93%A5</a><br />\n<br />\n於 2019 年 10 月 10 日，一張法庭破產令（HB263/2019）於網上流傳，破產令上所載破產人士姓名及職業，均與涉事的士司機一致。故此，本人現向破產管理署查詢，上列兩名均為鄭國泉之男子，是否同一人，如是，本人現向 貴署投訴，鄭國泉於破產令期間，管有貴重私人財產、虛報收入、以及接受饋贈。<br />\n<br />\n基於事態嚴重，敬請從速及慎重處理。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\nXxx<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucSoKhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucSoKhA.jpg&h=645428fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9f2fph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9f2fph.jpg&h=70b7b6ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b1865573c7c8da82a7f79700762f095a34a007b","tid":1646959,"uid":182452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed6b629054903163128a440fc1cdb018c9b11b92","tid":1646959,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59c814da6b890f68bf8ed35ca2b079d80508674e","tid":1646959,"uid":21972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8NXb9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8NXb9O.jpg&h=3b74b915&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}